---
title: Maple-Mustard Roasted Chicken and Shrimp With Herbed Wild Rice and Buttery Veg Trio
description: This chicken dinner benefits from the powerhouse flavour duo of maple and mustard. Herb-spiked wild rice and a slick side of shrimp, glazed carrots, radishes and snap peas round out this familiar and comforting meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-roti-a-la-moutarde-et-a-lerable-et-crevettes-de74df98.jpg
